&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About This Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We are hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager of Operations and&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;University Relationships&lt;/strong&gt; to own operations and grow University Partnerships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a senior, high-impact role for someone who operates comfortably with university leadership, understands the commercial and strategic drivers of international recruitment, and can turn strong relationships into measurable, long-term value.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The role goes beyond relationship management. You will act as a strategic partner, commercial negotiator, and long-term relationship owner, ensuring partnerships are:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;High-performing today&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Strategically aligned for the future&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Commercially strong and defensible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
